FROM "Tasks" AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t0."TaskId", t0."TagId", t1."Id", t1."Name"

FROM "Tasks" AS t
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT t0."TaskId", t0."TagId", t1."Id", t1."Name"
    FROM "TaskTags" AS t0
    INNER JOIN "Tags" AS t1 ON t0."TagId" = t1."Id"
) AS s ON t."Id" = s."TaskId"
LEFT JOIN "TaskTags" AS t2 ON t."Id" = t2."TaskId"
LEFT JOIN "TaskAttachments" AS t3 ON t."Id" = t3."TaskId"
LEFT JOIN "TaskAttachments" AS t4 ON t."Id" = t4."TaskId"
ORDER BY t."Id", s."TaskId", s."TagId", s."Id", t2."TaskId", t2."TagId", t3."Id"
